    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut <strong>half</strong> of your <strong>potatoes </strong>(skins on) into chips</p><p>Chop the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>potato[es]</strong> (skins on) into small cubes</p><p>Add the <strong>chips</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a small pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray[s] in the oven for 20-25 min or until golden and crisp</p>",
