    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>brioche bun[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Brush the <strong>brioche lid[s]</strong> with the <strong>remaining pambazo sauce</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>brioche halves</strong> to a baking tray (or two!), then put the tray[s] in the oven for 4-5 min or until warmed through</p>",
      "order": 6,
