    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To assemble, fill each <strong>warmed brioche bun </strong>with a little <strong>shredded lettuce</strong>, the <strong>pambazo filling</strong>, <strong>quick-pickled onion </strong>and a dollop of <strong>feta mayo</strong> – this is your <strong>Mexican-style pambazo</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>chips</strong> and <strong>remaining shredded lettuce</strong> to the side with the <strong>reserved pickling liquid </strong>drizzled over the top</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
